  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Whisk the eggs in a large bowl and season with salt and pepper.",
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion, carrot, and celery and cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the halved grape tomatoes to the skillet and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Pour the whisked eggs over the vegetables in the skillet.",
    "Transfer the skillet to the preheated oven and bake for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove the skillet from the oven and let it cool for 5 minutes.",
    "Slide the frittata onto a slate tile and serve warm."
